{"actor":"Rhen Khong","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T11:21:19Z","event_type":"updated","id":92,"issue_id":"GMMEM-5li","new_value":"{\"acceptance_criteria\":\"1. rg \\\"\\\\bclaude-mem\\\\b\\\" packages/ returns 0 hits (except data dir/db path constants and upstream attribution)\\n2. npm test passes, count \\u003e= Phase 0b baseline\\n3. npm run build-and-sync completes cleanly\\n4. MCP prompts/list returns 4 skill prompts (totalmem-search, totalmem-plan, totalmem-execute, totalmem-explore)\\n5. MCP resources/list returns 2 resources (totalmem://context/*, totalmem://sessions/recent)\\n6. CLAUDE_MEM_WORKER_PORT=37778 npm start works with deprecation log\\n7. CI green on test branch push (.github/workflows/ passes)\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"GMMEM-5li\",\"title\":\"Migrate claude-mem to totalmem: MCP-first architecture\",\"description\":\"Fork claude-mem as totalmem under totalmem-ai/totalmem org. Shift from Claude-plugin-first to MCP-server-first architecture so any MCP-compatible CLI (Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Cursor, Qwen, Codex) can use totalmem without platform-specific plugin installation. Data dir stays ~/.claude-mem/ in v1. Env var prefix changes CLAUDE_MEM_ → TOTALMEM_ with fallback. MCP server gains prompts + resources capabilities. All branding, package names, docs URLs updated.\",\"design\":\"7-phase plan: 0=research+baseline, 1=monorepo restructure (packages/core + packages/cli-adapters/*), 2=MCP enhance (prompts+resources), 3=rename core identity, 4=rename branding+tags, 5=rename docs+URLs, 6=multi-CLI installer, 7=tests+build. Phases 4+5 parallelize via separate branches. Phase 6 gated by Phase 0a research. P50 estimate 18h, P90 28h. Rollback: git reset HEAD~1 on \\u003e20 test failures.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"1. rg \\\"\\\\bclaude-mem\\\\b\\\" packages/ returns 0 hits (except data dir/db path constants and upstream attribution)\\n2. npm test passes, count \\u003e= Phase 0b baseline\\n3. npm run build-and-sync completes cleanly\\n4. MCP prompts/list returns 4 skill prompts (totalmem-search, totalmem-plan, totalmem-execute, totalmem-explore)\\n5. MCP resources/list returns 2 resources (totalmem://context/*, totalmem://sessions/recent)\\n6. CLAUDE_MEM_WORKER_PORT=37778 npm start works with deprecation log\\n7. CI green on test branch push\",\"notes\":\"P50=18h, P90=28h. If hitting P90, descope Phase 6 (multi-CLI installer) to follow-up. [Generated by /beadify]\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"epic\",\"owner\":\"127654909+AgileInnov8tor@users.noreply.github.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":1080,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-05T04:18:53Z\",\"created_by\":\"Rhen Khong\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T04:18:53Z\"}"}
